Title: The Collection of Passenger Name Records for Counterterrorism – Dawudi.ch
Description: IntroductionIn spring 2022, the Swiss Federal Police Fedpol proposed a law allowing for the collection of Passenger Name Records PNR from airline companies for the purpose of combating transnational terrorism and serious crime.
